﻿​​We invest in people and products that make your life better.
















Maywic Select Investments is an early stage and growth stage investor in consumer products and retail that promote healthy lifestyles, wellness, and well-being.​Founded by entrepreneurs and rooted in lifelong friendships, we support entrepreneurs who are bringing big ideas to life.



Maywic I is fully invested.We have now activated Maywic II

































