Criteria-   Outstanding management with a track record and a thorough understanding of the business-   Committed operating leadership with time, money, emotion, and reputation invested in the company -   Positive chemistry and synergy with the operating team-   The company should be advancing into real economic growth and critical mass - arithmetic to geometry-   A straightforward, easy to understand value proposition-   Positive instinct for the deal-   The company has a clear market niche and products that compete on more than just pricing

































