MAYWIC Select Investments II L.P. $25,000,000 Financing
MAYWIC Select Investments II L.P. just submitted form D announcing $25,000,000 equity financing.  This is a new filing. MAYWIC Select Investments II L.P. was able to sell $0. That is 0% of the round of financing. The total private offering amount was $25,000,000. The financing was made by 0 investors. Minimal accepted investment was $250,000. The financing document was filed on 2016-10-18. MAYWIC Select Investments II L.P. is based in  312 WALNUT STREET, SUITE 1151  CINCINNATI 45202. The firm's business is Pooled Investment Fund. The firm's revenue range is Decline to Disclose. The form was signed by  Frederic Mayerson.





